<a href="/wiki/List_of_X-Men_members#X-Men-In-Training_(2006–present)" title="List of X-Men members">X-Men-In-Training</a><br /><a href="/wiki/List_of_Xavier_Institute_students_and_staff#Students" title="List of Xavier Institute students and staff">Jean Grey School Students</a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="width: 40%;">Abilities</th><td>Retractable armored plates<br />Psionic matter manifestation</td></tr></tbody></table>
<p><b>Indra</b> (<b>Paras Gavaskar</b>) is a <a href="/wiki/Fictional_character" class="mw-redirect" title="Fictional character">fictional character</a> appearing in <a href="/wiki/American_comic_book" title="American comic book">American comic books</a> published by <a href="/wiki/Marvel_Comics" title="Marvel Comics">Marvel Comics</a>. A teenage <a href="/wiki/Mutant_(Marvel_Comics)" title="Mutant (Marvel Comics)">mutant</a>, Indra attended the <a href="/wiki/X-Mansion" title="X-Mansion">Xavier Institute</a> before its closing and is a member of the X-Men's training squad.  He first appeared in <i>New X-Men: Academy X</i> #7.
</p>
